{"tid":1546244,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地知唔知黑衫黑褲唔係dress code黎???????","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:06:36.000Z","uid":298658,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cde29a5e216d0955857d782df3b5d580fefe0206","tid":1546244,"uid":298658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"係啊，&quot;black bloc&quot;啊，知唔知咩叫black bloc?<br />\n<br />\n引用維基<br />\nA black bloc is a tactic used by groups of protesters who wear black clothing, ski masks, scarves, sunglasses, motorcycle helmets with padding, or other face-concealing and face-protecting items.[1][2] The clothing is used to conceal wearers' identities and <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">hinder criminal prosecution by making it difficult to distinguish between participants[/size=4]</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦，我想講乜?<br />\n我相信唔單止一個人有諗過/發現black bloc有時變左負累。<br />\n9月1大搜捕係最佳例子，個個都要搵衫換。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBlack bloc原意係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令人分唔到你係邊個</span></span></strong>。<br />\nE家變成左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">一望就知你係咩人</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想講嘅係，用black bloc之前諗清諗楚呢個係咩行動。<br />\n<br />\n勇武行動，攻立法會，拆狗屋，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必須black bloc</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n合法集會，合法測試交通，[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>black bloc係負累</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意我強調緊嘅係犯刑事嘅行動。合法嘅行動，絕對唔需要亦唔應該black bloc。<br />\n有人即刻話，堆曱甴都唔會跟法例架啦。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯啊，班曱甴係唔會跟法例架──正正係唔會跟法例，者係你着乜色衫佢都可以逗你搜你身扣你48個鐘，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁你仲black bloc增加自己比人逗嘅風險黎做乜?</span></strong> Black bloc係增加緊上法庭告得你入嘅成本咋，唔係幫你攔狗啊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上嘅野可能有好多人講屌係人都知啦<br />\n但事實上就係好多人已經當左黑衫褲係dress code而唔係戰略<br />\n例如9月5港大醫學院人鏈行動<br />\n9月1測試交通(我知9月1有人真係衝，但更大部份真係外圍搭下巴士咋)<br />\n<br />\n自己反思參透下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 當然，你想特登平時都着黑衫作為對抗白色恐怖嘅手段，冇問題都尊敬你咁做，不過要預左比曱甴逗"},{"pid":"6d2d94d9049645a1916ff910be1685e03d0218ea","tid":1546244,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d644656b5040431f71ce53b79e16c0d41efd79ca","tid":1546244,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOry9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=d74080dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"4a647a46b305300517a6804de66e39f950d7e76e","tid":1546244,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83107e447fc4e8a4f65f498c80158e7ef19f284c","tid":1546244,"uid":298658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:13:09.000Z","msg":"屌唔小心放大埋個size=4 code 好柒 大家當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e10700814bf891af58c218569cd5b1cdb1ca55","tid":1546244,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep